00:03:13.920 --> 00:03:14.960
are no longer brothers.

00:03:14.960 --> 00:03:17.800
Don't think that because the Tang army recaptured Chang'an,

00:03:17.800 --> 00:03:19.280
victory is assured.

00:03:20.200 --> 00:03:22.640
Once I deliver the Night Firefly Map to Lord Shi,

00:03:22.640 --> 00:03:24.570
he will surely achieve greatness.

00:03:24.880 --> 00:03:25.280
You...

00:03:25.400 --> 00:03:26.260
Master Zhuang,

00:03:26.880 --> 00:03:27.520
do you really think

00:03:27.520 --> 00:03:30.320
the Night Firefly Map is completely in your hands?

00:03:30.520 --> 00:03:32.520
Why don't you look at Chen Jingbian in the carriage?

00:03:32.520 --> 00:03:33.579
What state is he in?

00:03:35.800 --> 00:03:38.560
This is exactly how I want him to be.

00:03:39.800 --> 00:03:41.400
Don't foolishly think you can understand the formula

00:03:41.400 --> 00:03:43.000
by knowing the ingredients.

00:03:43.280 --> 00:03:44.880
You only know half the story.

00:03:45.920 --> 00:03:48.360
Though Tianshan Fire Poison can relieve pain,

00:03:48.360 --> 00:03:49.800
long-term overuse

00:03:50.160 --> 00:03:52.640
can lead to confusion and manipulation by others,

00:03:52.640 --> 00:03:53.840
or worse, delirium

00:03:54.400 --> 00:03:55.860
and death from poisoning.

00:03:56.920 --> 00:03:58.650
I'd like to ask you, Mr. Zhuang,

00:03:58.920 --> 00:04:01.080
how can you be certain which of Chen Jingbian's words

00:04:01.080 --> 00:04:01.840
are true

00:04:02.000 --> 00:04:03.130
and which are false?

00:04:03.360 --> 00:04:04.520
And how can you manage

00:04:04.520 --> 00:04:05.520
to continue administering medicine

00:04:05.520 --> 00:04:06.800
to prolong his illness

00:04:07.040 --> 00:04:10.100
rather than sending him to his grave with a single bowl?

00:04:17.040 --> 00:04:17.959
Miss Feng.

00:04:19.399 --> 00:04:20.839
I truly admire you.

00:04:21.360 --> 00:04:24.090
Only you can use medicine with such divine skill.

00:04:24.480 --> 00:04:25.340
How about this?

00:04:25.400 --> 00:04:27.060
Come with me to serve Lord Shi,

00:04:27.600 --> 00:04:30.330
and we'll share wealth and prosperity together.

00:04:30.560 --> 00:04:31.420
What do you say?

00:04:31.880 --> 00:04:32.440
Never.

00:04:34.400 --> 00:04:35.000
Lord Chen.

00:04:35.840 --> 00:04:36.970
Why don't you tell us

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:40.460
where that jade dagger given to Su Changming

00:04:41.000 --> 00:04:42.080
came from?

00:04:43.960 --> 00:04:44.520
And also,

00:04:45.080 --> 00:04:45.760
who was it

00:04:46.600 --> 00:04:49.659
who brought Feng Jianye's head and that precious sword

00:04:50.320 --> 00:04:51.440
to you?

00:04:55.159 --> 00:04:55.690
It was...

00:04:56.840 --> 00:04:58.280
It was Li Ling.

00:05:01.880 --> 00:05:03.240
Officer Li.

00:05:03.960 --> 00:05:05.080
You're here.

00:05:07.080 --> 00:05:09.120
You killed the man.

00:05:09.520 --> 00:05:11.440
You delivered the head.

00:05:11.960 --> 00:05:13.200
This grand gift,

00:05:13.800 --> 00:05:16.800
I gladly accepted it.

00:05:17.800 --> 00:05:19.320
You killed the man.

00:05:19.920 --> 00:05:21.600
You delivered the head.

00:05:21.880 --> 00:05:23.720
Li Ling, tell us,

00:05:24.440 --> 00:05:25.760
Feng Jianye,

00:05:25.840 --> 00:05:28.200
