00:05:28.200 --> 00:05:28.760
Impossible.

00:05:28.760 --> 00:05:30.400
Who really killed him?

00:05:30.400 --> 00:05:31.660
How could this happen?

00:05:32.520 --> 00:05:35.040
Li Ling, say something! Speak up!

00:05:40.840 --> 00:05:42.400
You kept saying

00:05:42.760 --> 00:05:45.159
General Feng's kindness to you was as great as mountains.

00:05:45.159 --> 00:05:46.220
But what about you?

00:05:46.520 --> 00:05:48.640
You did it for your own fame and fortune,

00:05:48.640 --> 00:05:50.120
