00:06:07.440 --> 00:06:08.240
Take revenge.

00:06:16.720 --> 00:06:17.320
Kill him.

00:06:18.240 --> 00:06:18.970
Come with me.

00:06:22.160 --> 00:06:22.640
Why?

00:06:23.400 --> 00:06:24.160
Why?

